<div class="note-source" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0031-sn">

   <p>
<abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Document: a document (not a letter) neither in the author's handwriting nor signed by the author ]">D</abbr>, <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span>.
 See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-06-02-0026" class="document">Orderly Book, 21 September24 November 1758.</a></p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-06-02-0031-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0031-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>They cheated and robbed king and country by deserting from their military units (<a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-06-02-0030" class="document">Orderly Book, 24 Sept.</a>).</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-06-02-0031-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0031-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>See the chart and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-06-02-0028&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-06-02-0028-fn-0005#GEWN-02-06-02-0028-fn-0005" class="document">note 5, Orderly Book, 22 September</a>.</p>

